@startuml 8_pwa_constraints

title 【⑧ 純 PWA】 採用時の足切り項目(できないこと)

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"

rectangle "PWA で実現不可な要件\n(1つでも該当 → PWA 採用不可)" as RECT #FFEBEE {
  card "IV3  BT Classic" as BT
  card "IV6  NFC HCE" as NFC_HCE
  card "IV9  DataWedge Intent API" as DW_INTENT
  card "IV10 UHF RFID" as RFID
  card "IV11 プリンタ(BT/USB)" as PRINTER
  card "IV14 赤外線(IR Blaster)" as IR
  card "IV15 シリアル(RS-232C 直)" as SERIAL
  card "IV16 Wi-Fi Direct" as WIFI_DIRECT
  card "IV18 UWB" as UWB
  card "IV19 ANT+ / Zigbee / Thread / Matter" as IOT
  card "IV20 オーディオジャック周辺機器" as AUDIO
  card "IV23 MSR(磁気カード)" as MSR
  card "VI3  Foreground Service(8h 常駐)" as FG
  card "VII2 ハードウェアキーストア" as KS
  card "VII4 証明書ピン留め" as PIN
  card "VIII6 ホーム画面ウィジェット" as WIDGET
  card "X2   MDM App Config 注入" as MDM
  card "X4   Device Owner 連携" as DO
}

note bottom
  iOS Safari で追加的に利用不可になる Web API:
    Web Bluetooth、Web NFC、Web USB、Web Serial
  ⇒ Android 単独運用でも、これらが必要なら PWA 不可
end note

@enduml
